snippet.textDisplay:
It is so refreshing to see this time you havent relied on stereotypical regional Rabab and Tappa style folk music. You are showing the modern and upbeat face of Pukhtoon culture with its undetachable heritage of Spelani, gemstones, Qehwa,  Cheil (Swabi's Chaddar), Chitrali cap, waist coat, Peshawari chappal and sheen khaal (Tattoos) on ladies' faces all presented with a rendition of a better version of Camilla Cabello i.e. REHMA.....
Guess what.....b4 its release I had a hunch that the way Xulfi is thinking this time he will definitely go for Zahoor.....zabardast 🙌
